- content_for :title do "Report a Player" end

%section
    .page-header
        %h1.text-design
            Report a Player
            %a.btn.btn-primary.pull-right{:href => reports_path}
                %i.fa.fa-tasks
                All Reports
    .row
        .col-md-4
            %h4.text-design Screenshots / Videos
            .content
                %p Moderators <em>may not</em> punish based on screenshots, unless the alleged offense is chat-related.
            %p For example, video proof is always required for team griefing and hacking.
        .col-md-4
            %h4.text-design Make your videos unlisted
            .content
                %p Make your videos <strong>unlisted</strong>, not public or private.
            %p This ensures that the staff, and only the staff, will be able to view your video.
        .col-md-4
            %h4.text-design Thanks for your hard work
            %p The staff appreciates the time you take to gather evidence of rule-breakers.
            %p Thanks for your commitment to making this network a better place!
    .row
        .col-md-12{:style => "text-align: center;"}
            %h3.text-design Who are you reporting?
            .form-inline
                %input.typeahead.form-control#reports{:name => "search", :type => "text", :style => "margin-top: 0;"}
